  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからケンカなんてしてないんだってば。
あたし達はこれが普通なの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Like we said, we're not even fighting.
We're just being how we always are.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まあたしかにケンカに見えるかもしれないな。
ルビア、すぐ怒鳴るし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, it's true it might look like we're fighting.
Doesn't take much for you to start shouting.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウスがわかってくれないからでしょ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Because you just don't get it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>信じられねぇ。
この言い合いがケンカじゃねぇってのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's just no way.
You guys are telling me this
quarreling here isn't a fight?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ケンカって言えなくもないかもしれないけど
オレ達はこれでなんとかやっていけてる。
だから心配してくれなくていいよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You could call it a fight,
but we'll figure it out somehow.
So you don't have to worry about us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかった。
普通とはちょっとちがうけど
おまえらの絆は星五つだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha. Kinda different from what
I'd consider normal, but that bond
you guys have gets five stars!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ピーチパイ、もう半分しかないぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Only half of my peach pie is left...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
